U.S. President Joe Biden signed a nearly $40 billion aid package for Ukraine on Saturday, a huge percentage of which is for military assistance. But behind the U.S. "generosity" is nothing more than self-interest. Editor: Yuan Xin Chief editor: Ge Jing Managing director: Mei Yan (To submit cartoons and share story ideas or feedback on our cartoon page, please contact us at cartoon_opinions@cgtn.com)